{"tid":844743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（援交妹與雞的日小子）稱一切為了家庭 18歲女不敵男友慫恿賣淫","createTime":"2018-10-02T06:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T06:36:00.000Z","uid":167451,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6b2e6fbd9df22887f47b1f802cb71a23127dfd","tid":844743,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:04:03.000Z","msg":"浙江杭州一名18歲張姓女子，為了賺取兒子的「奶粉錢」，在饒姓男友慫恿下投身對方經營的賣淫組織。惟她在上周五（9月28日）接客期間被警方拘捕，一併落網的還有饒男，以及其他賣淫女及嫖客共22人。饒男與3名主犯已因涉組織賣淫被刑拘，案件目前仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方本月初收到市民舉報，稱喬司鎮葛家車村有女子招嫖，查明疑犯身份後，上周五在村內的某間浴室中，搗破該個賣淫組織。經查證實，該組織以饒男及其兄弟為首，兩人各自讓妻子、女友去浴室賣淫，並招募了多名同鄉加入組織。<br />\n<br />\n至於已為人母的張女，起初聽到饒男的要求時，感到頗不樂意。但利益熏心的饒男不斷勸誘，向張女表示：「讓你賺這個錢也是為了家庭，兒子以後還需要奶粉錢。」張女無奈之下，最後點頭答應。<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD-18%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%B5%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E6%85%AB%E6%81%BF%E8%B3%A3%E6%B7%AB-032957110.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%2587%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%2586%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD-18%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2595%25B5%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2585%25AB%25E6%2581%25BF%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25B7%25AB-032957110.html&d=GBi8YXmaH8y%2Brevsq%2Fz6V5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=88544cbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD-18%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%B5%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E6%85%AB%E6%81%BF%E8%B3%A3%E6%B7%AB-032957110.html</a><br />\n<br />\n發覺世界越變越怪，特別香港！ 好像冇人會識體諒d人做雞的苦況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個人留言只會話個男人又食又拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實個focus 位係咪應該探討下做雞背後的慘況！<br />\n<br />\n即使係d援交妹，都係甘笑d人做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f515042e47cad8d68bb10ddb4eeaf41ef09ff89","tid":844743,"uid":11962,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"你唔做雞我邊有錢...."},{"pid":"bba8d4994d4ee8256780626cb102a7a231047477","tid":844743,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:17:33.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"ae379510890b04337d52ea7b7b8425f951361298","tid":844743,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"做人就係咁撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"142af0008f238035532c7cb808977bc36753a633","tid":844743,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"樓主覺得自己甘心癡埋去個馬夫到嘅女人抵可憐？"},{"pid":"640c59ce85f7faf5676cd6ff8d719b2a6f5fd930","tid":844743,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"142af0008f238035532c7cb808977bc36753a633","tid":844743,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"樓主覺得自己甘心癡埋去個馬夫到嘅女人抵可憐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:36:00.000Z","msg":"男女可能心態好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}